<body style="padding-left:40px; padding-right:100px">
  <h1 style=" font-family:  helvetica ;
  color:  pink;
  text-align: center; 
  font-size: 100px;
  line-height:  0;
  margin-top:  70px;">SAMSARA</h1>
  <h3 style= "font-family: helvetica ;
  color:  black;
    text-align: center; 
  font-size: 30px;""> Age Range: 13+ </h3>
  <p style= "font-family:helvetica;
  font-size:30px; color:#DAA520;"><strong>THE RULES:</strong> </p>
    <ol style= "font-size: 23px; ">
      <li> <p> Start with a game of candyland, use the card, gingerbread men and board. </p> </li> 
  <li> <p> Each Player is dealt a hand of 7 cards, there is a minimum of 3 players, and a maximum of 4. 
    </p> </li> 
    
    <li> <p> Pick a gingerbread man which will represent your soul moving through the cycle of life.  </li>
  
    <li> <p> Make pairs of 4's of the same color by asking a player for a color. Each color represents a different
realm of samsara. Move through the realms by putting down a pair of 4 which cooresponds to a realm. </p> 
    </li> 
    <li> Get a new card each time you get one taken, each player should maintain a hand of at least 7 cards.</li>
</ol>   
   <ul   style="font-size:  23px;
  padding-top:  10px; 
  padding-left:  70px;" >
     <li><p style="color:#FF0000";>Red = Nana Nutt's House aka Hell. This is where players will endure eternal suffering from thier very serious peanut allergy.</p></li>
    <li> 
  <p style="color:blue;">Blue = Peppermint Forest aka The Realm of the Hungry Ghosts. Players present in this realm are constantly looking for satisfaction in life through induldging their cravings which will never fully be satisfied.</p>
       </li>
<li> 
  <p style="color:purple;">Purple =  Licorice Lagoon aka The Realm of the Titans. You are sent to this realm because of your hate and jealousy. You will live trapped just below the human realm (King Kandy's Castle) surrounded by a dark, bitter licorice lagoon with your only source of food being the gnarled licorice forest.</p>
  </li>
  <li> 
  <p style="color:#DAA520;">Yellow = Lollipop Palace aka The Animal Realm. Here you will live comfortably in a land of sweet lollipops. Stay here as long as you please, your main characteristic as an animal is ignorance.</p>
    </li>
    <li>
  <p style="color:orange;">Orange = Frosted Palace aka The realm of Devas (Gods). Here you will enjoy a great life surrounded by luxury and ultimately privilege which will blind you from the suffering of those in other realms. You will live a long, nice life but will eventually die and be reborn.</p>
      </li>
    <li>
  <p style="color:green;">Green = King Kandy's Palace aka The Human Realm. Here you may leave Samsara (the cycle of life). You have the possibility of reaching enlightenment if you finish in this realm and have gone through the most realms.</p>
      </li></ul>
    
